# Local-only secrets (copy to `.env` — see `.gitignore`). Never commit real tokens.
#
# Used by: `scripts/gh-pr-push-merge.ps1` and `scripts/gh-pr-push-merge.sh`
# (optional — `gh auth login` keyring works without this).
#
# GitHub CLI accepts GITHUB_TOKEN; GH_TOKEN is copied to GITHUB_TOKEN by the scripts.
# Classic PAT: `repo` scope. Fine-grained: Contents + Pull requests for this repository.
#
# GH_TOKEN=ghp_xxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxx
